                  <summary>Surah 48:25-29 and 48:29-49:7 (Kufan system)</summary>
                  <msItemStruct>
                     <note type="general">Each new surah begins on a new line with no extra spacing and the initial formula receives no more attention than the text proper that follows in the same line.  A small circle marks the end of a verse.</note>
                     <note type="general">Location: Oriental Institute</note>
                     <note type="general">Pub. status: Published: recto and verso</note>
